description:
Get in the Halloween spirit with these terrifying episodes of Ghost Adventures, as Zak Bagans and the crew investigate dark and dangerous spirits inside the Trans-Alleghany Lunatic Asylum, the Hunedoara Castle where Vlad the Impaler was imprisoned, a 100-year-old cement factory turned into a Halloween attraction, an infamous Irish castle, and a bridge along route 666.

Stream Full Episodes of Ghost Adventures:
https://www.discoveryplus.com/show/ghost-adventures

#Discovery #GhostAdventures

About Ghost Adventures:
Zak Bagans and his crew investigate the most haunted places in the world. During the dusk-to-dawn lockdown, key evidence is documented to uncover the truth behind paranormal activity.
